\section{Licenses \& prices} 
Licenses are detailed in table \ref{tab:prices}.
\begin{table}[h]
\begin{center}
\begin{tabular}{|p{2cm}||p{1cm}|p{2cm}|p{2.5cm}|p{1.8cm}|p{1.9cm}|}
\hline
    {\bf License} & {\bf price} & {\bf users} & {\bf use} & {\bf updates} & {\bf maintenance}\\
\hline
\hline
Evaluation license (see section \ref{sec:evaluation}) & free & 1 designated & evaluation & n/a & n/a \\
\hline
Research license (see section \ref{sec:academic}) & \euros{600} & 1 designated
    & research & free (see section \ref{sec:updates}) & 15\% (see section
    \ref{sec:maintenance})\\
\hline
Education license (see section \ref{sec:academic}) & \euros{1800} & 1 designated
    & research, education & free (see section \ref{sec:updates}) & 15\% (see section
    \ref{sec:maintenance})\\
\hline
Development license & \euros{600} & 1 designated
    & development, no commercial use & free (see section \ref{sec:updates}) &
    15\% (see section \ref{sec:maintenance})\\
\hline
Production license (see section \ref{sec:production})& \euros{2400} & 1 designated
    & production on a single CPU, no redistribution & free (see section \ref{sec:updates}) &
    15\% (see section \ref{sec:maintenance})\\
\hline
\end{tabular}
\caption{\label{tab:prices}{\jcs} licenses \& prices}
\end{center}
\end{table}

\section{Evaluation licenses}
\label{sec:evaluation}
Evaluations licenses are valid 15 days and can be requested only once per
institution.

\section{Academic licenses}
\label{sec:academic}
Academic (education or research) licenses are granted to researchers and
teachers working in public research centers and universities, 
and can be used to do research.
 
Education licenses can be shared with the students attending the course.

\section{Production licenses}
\label{sec:production}
Production licenses are assigned to designated users. For server based
production licenses, please contact {\tt sales@koalog.com}.

Redistribution of the software is not allowed without Koalog's written
agreement.

\section{Updates}
\label{sec:updates}
Updates are free when the minor version number changes and the major
version number remains the same, otherwise they costs 50\%
of the price of the license.

\section{Maintenance}
\label{sec:maintenance}
The first year of maintenance is free of charge. Each following year, the
maintenance is charged 15\% of the license price.

%----------------------------------------------------------------------------
\section{More information} 
Contact {\tt sales@koalog.com} for special licensing schemes, redistribution,
volume discount.

